@ConstruX.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5182

# Auth Endpoint Tests
### Sign In
POST {{ConstruX.API_HostAddress}}/api/Auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "username": "ahmet.yilmaz",
  "password": "ahmet123"
}

### Sign Up
POST {{ConstruX.API_HostAddress}}/api/Auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Worker",
  "tradeSpecialty": "Operator",
  "hourlyRate": 25.0,
  "username": "test.worker",
  "password": "testpassword123"
}

###

# Labor Endpoint Authorization Tests
### Get All (Admin - Expect 200)
GET {{ConstruX.API_HostAddress}}/api/Labor
X-Worker-Id: 1
Accept: application/json

### Get All (Non-Admin - Expect 403)
GET {{ConstruX.API_HostAddress}}/api/Labor
X-Worker-Id: 2
Accept: application/json

### Get Self (Expect 200)
GET {{ConstruX.API_HostAddress}}/api/Labor/2
X-Worker-Id: 2
Accept: application/json

### Get Other (Non-Admin - Expect 403)
GET {{ConstruX.API_HostAddress}}/api/Labor/3
X-Worker-Id: 2
Accept: application/json

### Get Other (Admin - Expect 200)
GET {{ConstruX.API_HostAddress}}/api/Labor/3
X-Worker-Id: 1
Accept: application/json

### Create Labor (Non-Admin - Expect 403)
POST {{ConstruX.API_HostAddress}}/api/Labor
X-Worker-Id: 2
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Unauthorized Worker",
  "tradeSpecialty": "Beton İşçisi",
  "hourlyRate": 20.0,
  "username": "unauthorized",
  "password": "password123",
  "isAdmin": false
}
